OL,3,C'One in three kids' missing out on
OL,4,Cschool trips due to cost
OL,6,FSchool is almost out for summer and
OL,7,Fthis last week of term is often time
OL,8,Ffor pupils to enjoy that big
OL,9,Fresidential trip or a week of outdoor
OL,10,Factivities.
OL,12,FHowever, a survey of 1,000 parents by
OL,13,FZurich Municipal, seen by ITV News,
OL,14,Fclaims that one third of families now
OL,15,Fdeem school trips to be too expensive.
OL,16,FIt also reveals the average day trip
OL,17,Faway from school is now #28 per pupil,
OL,18,Frising to #430 for an overnight
OL,19,Fresidential.
