OL,3,C'One in three kids' missing out on
OL,4,Cschool trips due to cost
OL,6,FAtlantic Academy in Portland, Dorset
OL,7,Fholds an annual trip for their Year 6
OL,8,Fpupils to London each July. Their
OL,9,Fhighest number ever is missing this
OL,10,Fyear, with one in three parents
OL,11,Fchoosing not to fund the trip.
OL,13,FThe cost has jumped from approximately
OL,14,Fdoubled from #200 before 2019 more
OL,15,Fthan #400 now. Factoring in spending
OL,16,Fmoney, the total cost for parents can
OL,17,Fnear #600.
OL,19,FLisa Hallett's son Theo is one of
OL,20,Fthose missing out, she told ITV News:
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
