OL,3,C'One in three kids' missing out on
OL,4,Cschool trips due to cost
OL,6,F"It's 600 for two nights and I
OL,7,Fgenuinely couldn't afford it.
OL,9,FIt feels awful because I thought it's
OL,10,Fnot fair that Theo should have to miss
OL,11,Fout, he was upset because he's not
OL,12,Fgoing with his friends.
OL,14,FAll of my children have been on school
OL,15,Ftrips in years gone by. It's just Theo
OL,16,Fnow that hasn't been able to go on it
OL,17,Fbecause of the price."
