OL,3,C'One in three kids' missing out on
OL,4,Cschool trips due to cost
OL,6,FThe National Association of Head
OL,7,FTeachers says that two thirds of
OL,8,Fschools now have to fundraise or seek
OL,9,Fgrants to pay for extra curricular
OL,10,Factivities like school trips.
OL,12,FMelissa Heppell is the Principal at
OL,13,FAtlantic Academy and says the school
OL,14,Ftries to help parents where they can,
OL,15,Feven funding half a place for the most
OL,16,Fdeprived students if one or two in a
OL,17,Fclass can't cover the full expense.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
