OL,3,C'One in three kids' missing out on
OL,4,Cschool trips due to cost
OL,6,FHowever, rising costs of transport and
OL,7,Fattraction tickets means that many are
OL,8,Fmissing out on some important
OL,9,Fexperiences. Melissa said:
OL,11,F"It's really unfair and it's really
OL,12,Fsad that we have to leave so many
OL,13,Fchildren behind.
OL,15,FIt's not just one or two, we'd
OL,16,Fobviously look to support that. But we
OL,17,Fcan't when a significant chunk of
OL,18,Fchildren are left behind.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
