OL,3,C'One in three kids' missing out on
OL,4,Cschool trips due to cost
OL,6,F"When you consider that school trips
OL,7,Finvolve the actual payment of getting
OL,8,Finto the venue, but perhaps more
OL,9,Fcrucially the transport to get to the
OL,10,Fvenue, the cost of the fuel, the cost
OL,11,Fof the buses, all of that gets added
OL,12,Fonto the potential overall cost.
OL,14,FSchools haven't had the funding to
OL,15,Fsubsidise that cost or support young
OL,16,Fpeople to make sure that perhaps those
OL,17,Fpoor families can afford those
OL,18,Fopportunities that are available to
OL,19,Fthem."
